02:03:24.643 --> 02:03:27.520
But the rules of the game are laid down.

02:03:27.896 --> 02:03:30.940
We all have to play by them. Even me.

02:03:32.568 --> 02:03:36.195
It's all a mistake.
You've got to understand that.

02:03:37.072 --> 02:03:41.742
From the Department's point of view,
there was certainly a bit of an own goal.

02:03:41.827 --> 02:03:43.661
I'm not a terrorist.

02:03:44.288 --> 02:03:47.164
You know that. Please get me out of here!

02:03:47.666 --> 02:03:50.501
Sam, Information Retrieval is expensive.

02:03:51.003 --> 02:03:54.088
You're running up an enormous bill
by not cooperating.

02:03:56.508 --> 02:03:58.384
Please, Mr. Helpmann,

02:03:59.344 --> 02:04:01.137
help me find Jill.

02:04:06.685 --> 02:04:09.186
Sam, I think I ought to tell you.

02:04:10.314 --> 02:04:14.108
I'm afraid she's upped stumps
and retired to the pavilion.

02:04:16.653 --> 02:04:18.487
Thrown in the towel.

02:04:19.906 --> 02:04:21.073
Dead?

02:04:22.242 --> 02:04:23.367
Yes.

02:04:24.161 --> 02:04:28.623
It's all a bit confusing, but it seems
she was killed resisting arrest.

02:04:34.004 --> 02:04:36.380
No, it's all right. I did that.

02:04:39.718 --> 02:04:42.595
The odd thing is
it appears to have happened twice.

02:04:42.679 --> 02:04:45.389
A bit of a disputed call, I'm afraid.

02:04:47.517 --> 02:04:48.726
Twice?

02:04:49.978 --> 02:04:54.231
There you are. AII I can say is
don't fall at the last fence.

02:04:54.566 --> 02:04:57.735
The finish is in sight.
See you in the paddock.

02:04:58.070 --> 02:05:00.655
Do cooperate. Think of your mother.

02:05:00.864 --> 02:05:03.240
Good luck. Keep your eye on the ball.

02:05:03.325 --> 02:05:06.410
Got to go. Can't keep the orphans waiting.

02:05:16.004 --> 02:05:17.046
No!

02:05:35.357 --> 02:05:38.943
Don't fight it, son. Confess. Quickly.

02:05:40.278 --> 02:05:44.532
If you hold out too long,
you could jeopardize your credit rating.

02:06:35.375 --> 02:06:36.500
Jack?

02:06:45.635 --> 02:06:46.927
Shut up!

02:06:49.347 --> 02:06:51.932
Jack, I'm innocent. Please help me.

02:06:52.309 --> 02:06:53.601
Bastard!

02:06:56.146 --> 02:06:59.023
Jack, this is all a mistake. Please, Jack.

02:06:59.107 --> 02:07:00.900
Take that mask off.

02:07:06.239 --> 02:07:08.032
You stupid bastard!

02:07:09.993 --> 02:07:11.911
How could you do this to me?

02:07:12.078 --> 02:07:13.662
Jack, I'm frightened.

02:07:13.747 --> 02:07:16.290
How do you think I feel? You shit!

02:07:16.374 --> 02:07:18.042
- Jack...
- Shut up!

02:07:22.756 --> 02:07:26.967
This is a professional relationship.

02:07:30.972 --> 02:07:32.515
You can't!

02:07:34.768 --> 02:07:36.435
No, Jack, please!

02:08:25.902 --> 02:08:27.236
You okay?

02:08:27.362 --> 02:08:28.612
Tuttle!

02:08:29.155 --> 02:08:30.698
Call me Harry.

02:09:18.622 --> 02:09:19.955
Let's go!

02:14:30.183 --> 02:14:33.977
Mr. Lowry, so pleased you could make it.

02:14:34.270 --> 02:14:36.021
Right this way.

02:14:41.486 --> 02:14:43.153
It's a sad loss.

02:14:43.947 --> 02:14:46.114
Your mother was with her at the end.

02:14:50.578 --> 02:14:54.456
Mrs. Terrain has just received
that most wonderful of gifts.

02:14:55.667 --> 02:14:58.001
She came to us physically new.

02:14:58.670 --> 02:15:01.880
She goes hence from us
not so physically new.

02:15:01.965 --> 02:15:04.341
But the spirit never grows old.

02:15:05.927 --> 02:15:07.469
Madam Lowry!

02:15:11.975 --> 02:15:13.225
Mother!

02:15:14.852 --> 02:15:16.061
Sam!

02:15:17.939 --> 02:15:19.356
Mother?

02:15:21.234 --> 02:15:23.068
Stop calling me that.

02:15:25.238 --> 02:15:28.156
Mother, please!

02:15:28.658 --> 02:15:30.784
Is this guy bothering you?

02:15:31.995 --> 02:15:33.036
Mother!

02:15:34.580 --> 02:15:38.458
Go away. This is a very sacred moment.

02:18:48.316 --> 02:18:50.275
He's got away from us, Jack.

02:18:50.359 --> 02:18:53.653
I'm afraid you're right, Mr. Helpmann.
He's gone.

02:19:35.111 --> 02:19:38.656
<i>Tomorrow was another day</i>

02:19:40.117 --> 02:19:44.037
<i>The morning found me miles away</i>

02:19:45.331 --> 02:19:49.626
<i>With still a million things to say</i>

02:19:53.130 --> 02:19:55.382
<i>Now</i>

02:19:56.092 --> 02:20:00.387
<i>As twilight beams the sky above</i>

02:20:01.430 --> 02:20:04.849
<i>Recalling thrills of our love</i>

02:20:06.894 --> 02:20:10.897
<i>There's one thing I'm certain of</i>

02:20:11.649 --> 02:20:16.403
<i>Return I will</i>

02:20:18.239 --> 02:20:24.244
<i>To old Brazil</i>

